reviewText:
CONCRETE COWBOYS - I almost always enjoy a TOM SELLEC movie. This is no real exception. He always carries his character well even in his earlier movies.

SEEMED LIKE A GOOD IDEA AT THE TIME - JOHN CANDY does his usual hilariously good job in this movie.

I reccomend the purchase of this double feature for anyone who likes both actors. It is good clean entertainment as it was suppose to be.
